&lt;p>Sometimes, it&amp;rsquo;s more important to know what questions can be asked than to have the answers. So, take a moment to pause and think about how you would respond if you were in Sam Altman&amp;rsquo;s position.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Leaders aren&amp;rsquo;t born; they are shaped by their struggles, opportunities, and attitudes towards them. Regardless of whether you watch this interview or not, take 10 minutes to read or listen to these questions out loud to yourself. They will help you shape your thought process.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>